    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-blue-900 mb-8">About Our Library</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Our Library Management System is a modern digital gateway to explore the world of knowledge. 
            From seamless book tracking to an intelligent search feature, our system is designed to make your reading journey smoother and more engaging. 
            Join us in promoting literacy and lifelong learning in the digital age.
        </p>
